-# Helpers ===================================================================
.styleguide-section
  %h3{ :class => 'styleguide-section--title', :id => 'styleguide-section-helpers' } Page helpers
  %p.styleguide-section--description Helper classes allow you to add some helpful properties to specific elements on the page. For example, it's possible to pull image (or other element) to left, right or align it to the center by applying special align (pulls) classes. Each helper class has a description and use-case example.
  =partial( 'styleguide/elements/helpers/page' )

